content:
"Travel is the only thing you can buy that makes you richer." - Anonymous

"The world is a book and those who do not travel read only one page." - Saint Augustine

"Travel far, travel wide, and travel often. See the world, meet new people, and discover new cultures. The world is a big place and there is so much to see and experience." - Unknown

"Jobs fill your pocket, but adventures fill your soul." - Jaime Lyn Beatty

"Life is short and the world is wide." - Simon Raven

"Travel is the only thing you can buy that makes you richer." - Unknown
